{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-page-template-tsx","path":"/articles/MSRA-DKI-frontend-interview-experiences","result":{"pageContext":{"id":"MSRA-DKI-frontend-interview-experiences","lang":"cn","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开端"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2018年年底，看到很多同学都去实习了，虽然明知不可能正大光明去，而且MSRA在北京翘课去也很有风险，但算了算三个月也还是有可能，心一横还是先让学长帮忙把简历给了MSRA内部的组，不管怎么样可以体验一次真正的面试，可以为春招做准备。因为本人现在也就web前端比较稍微熟练一点，研究啥的根本没碰过，所以本来是打算投"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.msra.cn/zh-cn/jobs/interns/ieg-development-intern-20170512?language=chinese"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"创新工程组"}]},{"type":"text","value":"和"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.msra.cn/zh-cn/jobs/interns/ard-incubation-development-intern?language=chinese"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"创新孵化组"}]},{"type":"text","value":"的软件开发实习生去做做前端，没想到学长给投了"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DKI组（数据、知识、智能组）的"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，而且DKI组根本就没有在官网公开招工程方向的实习生，只开放个"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.msra.cn/zh-cn/jobs/interns/software-analytic-group-dki-intern?language=chinese"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"研究实习生"}]},{"type":"text","value":"的职位……经过一周时间的笔试和面试，"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"加上运气好和面试过程比较水的因素"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，拿到了梦寐以求的offer，但是却因为各种原因去不了，非常遗憾，可能这也是我人生中最近微软的一次了吧。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"笔试"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"元旦前发的简历，元旦后第二个工作日（星期四，2019年1月3日）就收到笔试通知了。笔试是要求根据自己对职位的选择选一个任务来做，并且"},{"type":"element","ta