e":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MDN"}]},{"type":"text","value":"），又不是闭卷。基本思想就是"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在onDragStart的时候记录下被拖拽的项目，然后在每个项目的onDragOver的时候，重新计算当被拖拽的项目拖到这个位置时的列表的顺序，然后更新下dom就行"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。由于我使用的react，所以直接把列表和被拖拽的项目记录在state里，更新的时候直接setState就可以了。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这里不使用onDrop而使用onDragOver的原因是需求要求"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在拖拽的过程中就能看到改变顺序时的效果"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有的同学看了API可能想到"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不记录被拖到的项目，而是把项目放在dataTransfer里传递"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，但是"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11065803/determine-what-is-being-dragged-from-dragenter-dragover-events"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"dataTransfer是不能在onDragOver的时候访问到的"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，所以必须自己记录和处理。而且需求还要求正常被拖动的项目"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不能在列表中显示"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，我这里耍了点小trick：被拖动的项目的color将会被设置成white，这样就达到了隐藏的效果~"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前端的要求应该还是比较简单的，加上从create-react-app建项目以及最后上传，也就做了2个小时左右吧，倒是写项目经历写了五六个小时……"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"面试"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"笔试提交当晚，就打电话来约面试时间了。面试最终是在第二周星期一（2019年1月7日下午），通过Skype进行的。面试分了以下几个阶段："}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前20分钟左右：算法题"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"题目：类似于"},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://leetcode.com/problems/number-of-islands"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Leetcode 200"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感受：最大的感受就三个字"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"运气好"}]},{"type":"text","value":"！！！！因为当天上午刚做过，而且这种题目就是那种"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"没做过死活不会，做过就会了"}]},{"type":"text","value":"的非常典型的题目（你看了就知道），写起来都是套路。和leetcode不同的一点是"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输入输出要自己处理"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，还好我还记得一点C++的输入输出的写法……"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"写完后那边还问了一个追加问题："},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果不是一次输入整个矩阵，而是要求每输入一行就输出当前输入的计算结果"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。最简单的粗暴的做法当然是"},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完全重跑一遍"}]},{"type":"text","value":"（当然不是最好的），后来在那边的启发下相处了一个稍微好一点的做法："},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"记录上一行的1所处岛的编号，然后遍历本行，当本行遇到一个1时，看上一行，若上一行周围3个位置只有一个1或者都是同一个岛或者左上和右上是同一个岛，那么本行的1是那个岛的一部分，结果不变；若左上和右上都是岛，但是不同的岛，说明这个1会连接这两个不同的岛，那么结果减1；如果上面都是0，说明这个岛是个新的，那么结果+1"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。最后想出来还是有点不太有底，但是面试官还是非常肯定这个做法。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"算法题运气实在是太好了，因为我最没底的就是算法，这次算法运气太好水过，也许下一次就挂了（嗯之前面试的另外一个组就直接挂在一面算法题……）……这也是为什么我有一种"},{"ty